  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to determine whether propranolol can decrease pain symptoms in a
      common subset of patients admitted to a trauma center after injury.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      The main purpose of this pilot study is to investigate Propranolol's utility in the trauma
      population. Specifically, to see if it reduces pain scores post-injury.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
